
#An adventure game similar to The Oregon Trail game, in which a main character 
and his group must travel across the country in the middle of a zombie apocalypse. 
The characters are attacked by various kinds of zombies, some fast, strong, flying, 
or large. The character must keep good storage of his food, and resist being killed 
between checkpoints, which are very far away. During the journey, the character can be
bitten, as well as his crew, and must be left behind. If a person is bitten they will
die. However, to prevent death, an antidote can be found however they are rare, and
difficult to obtain.
